{"tid":1842444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［以罷助罷］我準備好同醫護一齊罷工","createTime":"2020-01-25T16:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T02:18:51.000Z","uid":81236,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"49453b17c648b7c73200b7939de5800b62a07372","tid":1842444,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:36:47.000Z","msg":"香港人如果真想防疫<br />\n<br />\n就唔好再post班垃圾小粉紅係微博等等講啲咩<br />\n<br />\n而係要行動！<br />\n<br />\n罷工吧！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">以罷助罷，準備好同醫護一齊罷工<br />\n<br />\n齊對抗真正既萬惡之源<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港共政權</span><br />\n<br />\n因為香港沒有獨立，所以政府不用封關手段防疫<br />\n因為香港沒有普選，所以政府不用理會民眾所須<br />\n<br />\n如果醫護罷工，我願意出一分力同醫護一齊罷工<br />\n承受被炒既風險好過健康風險<br />\n<br />\n#以罷助罷"},{"pid":"38624070f7937b9eee856b255217de4b6ff093f2","tid":1842444,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"入去自推十連！要十分鐘內上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n請不要再說：「我支持醫護罷工。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842379</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"19a181100f5cbaa4dd6120b43ff8e1984b3f815a","tid":1842444,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"我準備好同醫護一齊罷工"},{"pid":"bd21344ce0e128ca55d279ff8c15f53d06d038cc","tid":1842444,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:38:02.000Z","msg":"請不要再說：「我支持醫護罷工。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842379</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"005826bf62beadc12944b144d99c3025f34d7a29","tid":1842444,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/977rMtW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F977rMtW.jpg&h=752334f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3z7bXAD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3z7bXAD.jpg&h=a4562288&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b1b8cd66fcbbbb68d9b6df075dabdf16cc65575","tid":1842444,"uid":106851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:39:35.000Z","msg":"全民三罷"},{"pid":"e733a11e2c595b6981ad494ad1493f8afaee5b29","tid":1842444,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">罷工唔止係醫護人員嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n係全香港700萬市民嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港三罷 刻不容緩</span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oisbVO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoisbVO4.jpg&h=e95b4412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔罷 下一個中招嘅好可能係你</div>"},{"pid":"20fb299b76e6498ea445f774ff2b504778bddc4c","tid":1842444,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aaabfc1796e64fba82284b82539eb847d24c2bf3","tid":1842444,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"試想<br />\n<br />\n今天出現武漢肺炎<br />\n明年可以有廣州腦炎<br />\n後年可以有北京眼炎<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎傳染性、死亡率有多高不是問題癥結<br />\n<br />\n真正問題在於一個不代表人民的政府<br />\n<br />\n香港如是，中國亦如是<br />\n<br />\n罷工、普選、獨立吧<br />\n<br />\n以制度選出一個代表人民的政府<br />\n<br />\n無論在政治、經濟、生活、健康<br />\n<br />\n都必定以人民的權利為依歸<br />\n<br />\n別再說政治唔關我事<br />\n<br />\n政治可以剝奪你的金錢、自由<br />\n<br />\n現在在剝奪你的健康"},{"pid":"ec36a5dceadb6c1c62b02d82298968e3c8ca297f","tid":1842444,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:44:01.000Z","msg":"我請求咁多位同你地既親人親口講一次罷工既原因<br />\n<br />\n係對抗真正既萬惡之源<br />\n<br />\n港共不除日後一樣可以漠視香港人既健康安全<br />\n<br />\n係fb, ig share<br />\n<br />\n每人同一個公司你最熟既同事講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439e24aba7d7a896e9d1e7bcb2170fd7d40fddfc","tid":1842444,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b1b8cd66fcbbbb68d9b6df075dabdf16cc65575","tid":1842444,"uid":106851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:39:35.000Z","msg":"全民三罷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:45:12.000Z","msg":"罷工只係手段<br />\n<br />\n政權係令到全港人受害既禍根"},{"pid":"c3dd1ccd70fef29fae27e3a86789c6be3c1f02cd","tid":1842444,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:45:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2894e6c7a6f2413e2ce7caa852099f78bfa3af30","tid":1842444,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"282536d6cc9cad182a9b3405ce8676562123cadd","tid":1842444,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e733a11e2c595b6981ad494ad1493f8afaee5b29","tid":1842444,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">罷工唔止係醫護人員嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n係全香港700萬市民嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港三罷 刻不容緩</span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oisbVO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoisbVO4.jpg&h=e95b4412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔罷 下一個中招嘅好可能係你</div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:48:50.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272dd84f11ffb6893780d631bbf3102489b8b8bc","tid":1842444,"uid":157117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:49:02.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"ca759c954ebc7cbc40d068b9e76965c06b2741fa","tid":1842444,"uid":157117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:49:13.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"746a7dbc8b0a14d3b2bc7c600c62d006bb877237","tid":1842444,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep